{"tid":2379433,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人已經好懷念食晚市？","createTime":"2021-01-25T08:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T12:18:23.000Z","uid":63048,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4be97e15d23c40c59fafd0c1654db3dd32f3ad","tid":2379433,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"之前係懷念去旅行，而家連上次食晚市係幾時都已經唔記得。<br />\n<br />\n食晚市通常時間長啲，餐廳供應多啲菜式，有 Wine Pairing，同埋氣氛好好多，令人容易放鬆，又可以係完成一日工作之後食個大餐咁。<br />\n<br />\n買外賣返屋企都係覺得食緊快餐，唔覺得係享受。"},{"pid":"6284e8c12a8eb8a5b475bb19fbb7f232bd9ed7ff","tid":2379433,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"懷念去夜市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b710db64fe77696b8dbafdcbfa768c8161d419","tid":2379433,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6284e8c12a8eb8a5b475bb19fbb7f232bd9ed7ff","tid":2379433,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"懷念去夜市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"唔洗懷念定仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e00e26b2fa4a02ae6ae88c68c87edba20e0b66","tid":2379433,"uid":276592,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:32:20.000Z","msg":"無，作為毒撚一向鍾意係屋企食多過出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376edf66818c2fc6e8f92f580d7b1d2352bd80c6","tid":2379433,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52e00e26b2fa4a02ae6ae88c68c87edba20e0b66","tid":2379433,"uid":276592,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:32:20.000Z","msg":"無，作為毒撚一向鍾意係屋企食多過出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"same<br />\n最好永遠都禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1de3a50b9c